Assignment :- To Create a Orphan process

    -> write a C prg to generate a Orphan process


        This programs creates a Orphan process in the system by forking a child process and then the Parent completes it's works and terminates, while in this child process become orphan and Os identifies this and assignes new parent process of init(pid = 1)/systemd(pid = 1412) and in my system only it may differs. 

To Build the Program run the command as follows
1) make
2) then run the orphan file
